otel in Midtown Manhattan. An ode to the Mad Men era, the project is designed through the lens of the golden age of advertising and the old-school glamour of New York City, setting the scene to capture the essence of mid-century New York with a playful twist. Fit for an indulgent midday martini, the space is also designed for dancing the night away. With a fully equipped DJ booth and state-of-the-art sound system; every moment is a celebration of the eclectic spirit."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"190da98fd565","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"069630c1d2a60","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"The Bolt Team carved out the space with moody intimate corners and lounge-like atmosphere. The design philosophy revolved around the tactile and the personal. Through layered patterns and meticulously selected textures, including rich cut velvets, fluted glass, decorative fringe, custom lighting, and millwork fabricated in Bolt’s workshop in Greenpoint, Brooklyn; every element was carefully selected and serves as a testament to their commitment to crafting an experience where comforting nostalgia is greeted with a contemporary touch."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"dea7e16fded5","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"0ac9a6a811680","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Agency of Record highlights Bolt’s capacity to harmonize design innovation with practical execution. As a licensed general contractor and utilizing their in-house fabrication team, Bolt Builds ensures high-quality craftsmanship and seamless integration at every stage, from dynamic lighting to bespoke elements."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"a36b3fbe770e","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"7fd912dc9356","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"\n"},{"_key":"72e7d597a2a3","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Articles about this project:"},{"_key":"60c76e8b3683","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"\n"},{"_key":"0dd591533b98","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Fox 5 News \nSecret NYC"},{"_key":"c0850c469d60","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"\n"},{"_key":"decb86ebef10","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Hotel Above Par"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"}],"descriptionPlaintext":"Agency of Record | A Sleek, Full-Service Interior by Bolt Builds\n\nLocated in Midtown Manhattan NYC, Agency of Record is a meticulously executed 3,000 sq ft interior completed in just 11 months. Bolt Builds, a Brooklyn-based design-build-fabrication studio, masterfully handled everything, from interior design, lighting design, rendering, and FF\u0026E sourcing to custom fabrication and full-service construction.\n\nAgency of Record is a cocktail lounge and restaurant nestled in the heart of the historic Renwick Hotel in Midtown Manhattan. An ode to the Mad Men era, the project is designed through the lens of the golden age of advertising and the old-school glamour of New York City, setting the scene to capture the essence of mid-century New York with a playful twist. Fit for an indulgent midday martini, the space is also designed for dancing the night away. With a fully equipped DJ booth and state-of-the-art sound system; every moment is a celebration of the eclectic spirit.\n\nThe Bolt Team carved out the space with moody intimate corners and lounge-like atmosphere. The design philosophy revolved around the tactile and the personal. Through layered patterns and meticulously selected textures, including rich cut velvets, fluted glass, decorative fringe, custom lighting, and millwork fabricated in Bolt’s workshop in Greenpoint, Brooklyn; every element was carefully selected and serves as a testament to their commitment to crafting an experience where comforting nostalgia is greeted with a contemporary touch.\n\nAgency of Record highlights Bolt’s capacity to harmonize design innovation with practical execution. As a licensed general contractor and utilizing their in-house fabrication team, Bolt Builds ensures high-quality craftsmanship and seamless integration at every stage, from dynamic lighting to bespoke elements.\n\n\nArticles about this project:\nFox 5 News \nSecret NYC\nHotel Above Par","featuredImage":{"_key":null,"_type":"image","asset":{"_id":"image-f5822f028a958941ea07f3262520c1e40b10f641-7367x4910-png","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","description":null,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"aspectRatio":1.50040733197556,"height":4910,"width":7367},"lqip":"data:image/png;base64,"},"tags":null},"caption":null,"crop":null},"images":[{"_key":"190e81b04aaf","_type":"projectImage","asset":{"_id":"image-b19a05c1b80c4ea34e212c5addc5fa5091920c01-2924x1950-jpg","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","description":null,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"aspectRatio":1.4994871794871796,"height":1950,"width":2924},"lqip":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"tags":null},"caption":null,"crop":null},{"_key":"e201e82f4c0e","_type":"projectImage","asset":{"_id":"image-12b009bb01cb51dd4599f05641db38b4f1452915-4379x6568-jpg","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","description":null,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"aspectRatio":0.6667174177831913,"height":6568,"width":4379},"lqip":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"tags":null},"caption":null,"crop":null},{"_key":"c5eb688cf4fb","_type":"projectImage","asset":{"_id":"image-ee5db42985b4843a5e6917e677cd9daa536d68de-5427x3618-jpg","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","description":null,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"aspectRatio":1.5,"height":3618,"width":5427},"lqip":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"tags":null},"caption":null,"crop":null},{"_key":"7d1e97fdd013","_type":"projectImage","asset":{"_id":"image-dee0867c4976b903d1b9704f22e9acf489223f56-6880x4587-jpg","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","description":null,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"aspectRatio":1.499890996293874,"height":4587,"width":6880},"lqip":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"tags":null},"caption":null,"crop":null},{"_key":"c5d6f74d5ce9","_type":"projectImage","asset":{"_id":"image-5b3851363c3485c7af62c93f48b4a11f5aa5030a-8034x5359-jpg","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","description":null,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"aspectRatio":1.4991602910